form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Title of the image, TAT CA MOI NGUOI TI NAM TU 17 TUOI TRE LON NHAP CANH VA HOA KY DUOC, Form number, Mau G-648 ( (6-2-75) Bo Tu' Phap Hoaa So Ngoai Kiieu va Nap Tich

full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/21/2023 TAT CA MOI NGUOI TI NAN TU 17 TUOI TRO LEN NHAP CANH VAO HOA KY DUOC COI NHU LA NGÜÖI VO QUOC TICH (PAROLE) PHAI NAP TO BAO DAM VA CHIU TRACH NHIEM VE TAI SAN CUA MINH. Toi, TRAN MAU NGOC THI xin the va khai rang: 1 Toi hien CO ky thac trong cac Ngan Han tai Hoa Ky va cac quoc gia khac mot so tien nhu sau: Dia Piem Ten Ngan Hang So Tien 2. Toi hien CO so tien ky quy tai Hoa Ky va cac nuoc khac tinh theo gia thi truong nhu sau: Cong ty/Co quan chanh phu So kho phan hoac tien ky quy Tri gia 3. Toi hien la so huu chu cua so bat dong san tai Hoa Ky va tai cac quoc gia khac nhu sau: Dia diem Tri gia Tinh ca nguon loi khai thac 4. Toi hien CO mot so ngoai tê vang, bac cuong, cac vat khac CO gia tri, va cac do My thuat tai Hoe Ky ve cac quoc gia khac Dia diem Tail Vat Tri gia 5. Toi la SÓ huu chu so tai vat bat dong san va tai vat ca nhah tai Hoa Ky va tai cac quoc gia khac, chua dudc liet ke tren day: Dia diem Tai vat Tri gia 6. Tong so tai vat tri gia nhu sau: Signature don Ky ten day du va chinh thuc cua duong Buong don voi ten tren day da tayen the tai ngay (ths2g/ngay/nsm Ten thong dich vien (viet bang chu in) Chui ky cua thong dich vien Chd ky va cap bac cua si quan) (Neu can, hay them nhung you to can thiet noi mat sau cua to khai nay) Mau G-648 (6-2-75) Bo Tu' Phap Hoa Ky So Ngoai Kiou va Nhap Tich Vietnamese
